        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Remote Worker Relief Act of 2020 </b></p> <p>This bill establishes rules for the taxation of wages of individual taxpayers who work remotely to comply with COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) requirements and for the taxation of the businesses for whom such taxpayers work. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
